# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
# http://davidlaing.com/2012/09/19/customise-your-gitattributes-to-become-a-git-ninja/
* text=auto

# Exif diffs for images
# Not convinced this output is particularly useful for me, but it is better than
# no diff at all.
*.png diff=exif
*.jpg diff=exif
